                     <interp inst="t18270913-345-person2518" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . He was not told to receive this money, and never paid it us; he did not return; I found him next day in Princes-street, dressed in new clothes; I asked what he had done with our truck; he said he gave a boy 6d. to bring it home, but it had not come; he said he had lost the money; that he put it on the truck while he fastened his cords, and forgot it for some time, and when he looked for it, it was gone.</p>
